Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防止这件事外传
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快把她找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早搜查组已到了马赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天之内应该会有消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕令也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 先找到其落脚点就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在暂时静观其变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不想回家的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信 看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁寄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很端正的字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经平安到达马赛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在大概在为自己做的事后怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜现在的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃洛伊丝夫人 是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻漂亮的贵妇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 能问你件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你在温室里看到维尔福夫人和伯爵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奥特伊听你说过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直很在意 那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的情人为什么是她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能认为他怀有某种目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 为什么他一看到你的症状就知道是中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…难道想说伯爵是真凶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有伯爵 我现在或许就不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说我 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么巧正好有解毒剂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找遍全巴黎也不可能有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是医生也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你当时救得了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为伯爵在 我才能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵去投毒有什么好处 你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽深的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解伯爵真面目的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Encyclopedie De La Toxicologie：『毒物学百科全书』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是感觉身体无力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为毒的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的体内已渗入大量毒素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵什么时候给你这个戒指的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 换个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个有印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的首饰盒里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是香水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算毁了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了无可挽回的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若世人知道我妻子居然犯下毒杀罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至今所取得的成就将会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的计划还没结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想杀多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在你计划之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也打算杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要有可爱的爱德华就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装得一副高高在上的圣人模样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的侮辱我无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您再对我说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就马上死给您看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重视脸面的检察官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不希望有这样的丑闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您…该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只能杀别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明早你将被送去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你准备了一个附铁栅栏的单人间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能有点窄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里结束你的一生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带上毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都了解伯爵的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您身体可安好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵看来也很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说瓦朗蒂娜小姐得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安在照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在在马赛疗养
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没等我们赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执事巴鲁瓦先生就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经救出了重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福夫人发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么维尔福家会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世上没有偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是因果报应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福家变成那样也是报应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我们在Luna相识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您或许认为那是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而命运中不存在所谓偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如那落日是大宇宙的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命运也是由无法动摇的必然所形成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的人生里不存在偶然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有强大的意志力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们接受偶然 为其所操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我则不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开拓了自己的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开拓了自己的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会与您相识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我才身在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我想改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为像您一样的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 阿尔贝先生我送您一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「等待 然后期待」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么傻坐在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮 你母亲怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没大碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过从那以后都不大精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说那个 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就要在歌剧院和交响乐团一起演奏钢琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在歌剧院？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 终于梦想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚接到通知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的琴艺被认可了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Musique De Chambre：室内音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我得回去练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前在奥特伊的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听得懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「岩窟王」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人送花来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亚·卡瓦尔坎蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐格拉尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎想解除你和欧仁妮的婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了确认她的心意
